summary:
Extensive professional working experience in international (cultural) organisations. Has created Fait Accompli with the aim to improve communication and business between Dutch and French companies/institutions by using her knowlegde of Dutch and French cultures and languages.

Specialities: Native-speaker French and perfectly fluent in Dutch, English and German. Support in strategic communication and business between French and Dutch partners or clients, matchmaking, market research.
